#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/mock.rst:2
msgid "Mock"
msgstr "模拟"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/mock.rst:4
msgid ""
"Simulates L2 storage with configurable size and bandwidth.  Useful for "
"testing the L2 pipeline without real storage hardware."
msgstr "模拟具有可配置大小和带宽的 L2 存储。适用于在无真实存储硬件的情况下对 L2 流水线进行测试。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/mock.rst:7
msgid "**Fields:**"
msgstr "**字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/mock.rst:9
msgid "``max_size_gb``: Maximum size in GB (> 0)."
msgstr "``max_size_gb``：最大容量（单位：GB，须大于 0）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/mock.rst:10
msgid "``mock_bandwidth_gb``: Simulated bandwidth in GB/sec (> 0)."
msgstr "``mock_bandwidth_gb``：模拟带宽（单位：GB/秒，须大于 0）。"

